branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series CV3 is a valve mounted, double acting cylinder. The operation style can be changed to normally retracted or normally extended. Built-in throttle valves are provided to enable speed adjustments in each direction. CV3 has six mounting options available and bore sizes range from 40mm to 100mm. The CV3 series is auto switch capable.
&lt;/p&gt;

